==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cover crop
<hw>Cov"er crop</hw>. <def>A catch crop planted, esp. in orchards. as a
protection to the soil in winter, as well as for the benefit of the soil
when plowed under in spring.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Covered</ent>⟦br⟧
